	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nihil plane est (reverende in Christo pater) quod scribam, et tamen inanes has mitto, ne d. consulem absque meis ad te dimitterem.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Habes tu hic homines certos, per quos, si quid aut <placeName ref="l41">Bernam</placeName>, <placeName ref="l167">Genevam</placeName> aut <placeName ref="l301">Lugdunum</placeName> scribere velis, id commodissime et rectissime possis.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Est in comitatu d. consulis simul cum <persName type="auto_name">Pellizariis</persName> clarissimus vir d. d. <persName type="auto_name">Guiziardus</persName>, qui aliquando d. d. <persName ref="p1283">Gesnero</persName> et mihi hospitium dedit Telii; itaque d. <persName ref="p1283">Gesnerus</persName> de illius adventu videtur commonendus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quo loco res nostrae sit, ex consule audies.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuas nullas dum accepi propterea, quod mercatores nostri <placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name">Tiguro</placeName> per <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2582">Feldkirchum</placeName> (quod ibi sit mercatus) redeunt; hanc nos putamus esse morae causam.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Scripsit proxime legatus d. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8160">de Bellievre</persName> spem magnam esse negotium <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l176">Glaronense</placeName> confectum iri.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quod utinam ita fiat aliquando!</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sed magna est hominum illorum ferocia, quae an compesci possit, ut nunc sunt mores hominum, dubito.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">D. consulem non est quod commendem, cum sit commendatus tibi alioquin.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Si quid acciderit, quod tua scire intersit, non deero officio.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Vale, reverende in Christo pater.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l98">Curię</placeName> 26. iunii anno 1564.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">T[uus] <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8009">Fab[ricius</persName>]</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="manual">Amplissimo viro d. <persName ref="p495" type="citizen_name">Heinrycho Bullingero</persName>, domino suo et in Christo patri reverendo.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name">Tiguri</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
	</text>
